# Landscape (in two way)
	1: layout Directory >new > layout Resource File
	2: (Orientation for preview (o)) > Creat Landscape Varition

# Night Mood
	1: Orientation for preview (o) > creat Other > Night Mode + night

# version
	1: Orientation for preview (o) > creat Other > Version + (API Number)

# TreadMark
	1: layout Directory >new > layout Resourcr File > name: TreadMark, RelativeLayout + OK
	2: <include layout ="@layout/treadMark"   (include another xml file.)


# center element
1: RMB > center > center Horizontaly.
